upport (GPT-4.1, Gemini 2.5, Claude Sonnet 3.7/4)\n- Multimodal (image) input support\n- Custom workflows and team sharing features\n\n**Wave 4 (March 5, 2025)**:\n- **Preview functionality** for instant code change visualization\n- **Tab to Import** feature for easier dependency management\n- **Cascade assistant** for intelligent next-step suggestions\n- **Linter integration** for real-time code quality checking\n\n### Recommendations:\n1. **Visit the official changelog** at `https://windsurf.com/changelog` for the most accurate and detailed February 2025 updates\n2. **Check the Windsurf Blog** at `windsurf.com/blog` for detailed release announcements\n3. **Follow official channels**: Twitter (@codeiumdev), Discord community, and GitHub release notes\n\nThe search results suggest Windsurf maintained an aggressive release schedule in early 2025 with monthly or more frequent updates, so February 2025 would have likely included incremental improvements between Waves 3 and 4.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
