},{\"title\":\"Devin 2.0 来袭：Cognition 将 AI 软件工程师月费从 500 美元大幅降至 20 美元\",\"url\":\"https://news.sina.cn/ai/2025-04-04/detail-ineryqsr1728101.d.html?fromsinago=824\"},{\"title\":\"51c大模型~合集121\",\"url\":\"https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_49587977/article/details/147519045\"},{\"title\":\"谷歌开放 Gemini 2.5 Pro 公测；微软推出 Azure AI Foundry 重大升级\",\"url\":\"http://app.myzaker.com/news/article.php?pk=67f323d78e9f09118c210850\"},{\"title\":\"Cognition\",\"url\":\"http://wap.hrtechchina.com/tag/cognition/\"},{\"title\":\"首位“AI软件工程师”亮相引爆科技圈\",\"url\":\"https://k.sina.cn/article_7857201856_1d45362c0019029pge.html\"},{\"title\":\"Cognition\",\"url\":\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Cognition/64159129\"},{\"title\":\"Cognition AI\",\"url\":\"https://baike.baidu.com/item/Cognition%2520AI/65820831\"},{\"title\":\"Cognition AI 逆势而上，融资 4 亿美元，估值达 102 亿美元\",\"url\":\"https://m.528btc.com/kx/1151181537.html\"}]\n\nBased on my web search, I was unable to find specific information about Devin AI updates released in **February 2025**. However, I found important information about Devin AI's recent developments:\n\n## Key Devin AI Updates (Early 2025)\n\n### **Devin 1.2 Release (Early 2025)**\nBefore the major 2.0 release, Cognition AI released **Devin 1.2** in early 2025 with the following enhancements:\n\n- **Enhanced Context Reasoning**: Improved ability to analyze codebases, identify patterns, and reuse existing code more effectively\n- **Voice Command Integration**: Users can now send voice messages through Slack to issue instructions to Devin, simplifying human-AI interaction\n\n### **Devin 2.0 Major Release (April 2025)**\nThe most significant update came in April 2025:\n\n**Pricing Changes:**\n- Drastic price reduction from **$500/month to $20/month** (96% reduction)\n- Hourly development cost of approximately **$11**, approaching human engineer hourly rates\n\n**New Features:**\n- **Native Agent IDE Platform**: Complete overhaul as a pure agent-native platform\n- **Parallel Development**: Support for concurrent development tasks\n- **Intelligent Planning**: Enhanced task planning and execution capabilities\n- **Cloud Multi-Instance IDE**: Integration of cloud-based multi-instance development environments\n- **Autonomous Code Correction**: Self-correcting code functionality\n- **Dynamic Documentation Management**: Automated documentation handling\n\n**Performance Improvements:**\n- According to internal benchmarks, the latest version shows an **83%+ improvement** in completing junior development tasks per Agent Compute Unit (ACU) compared to the previous version\n\n**New Tools:**\n- **Devin Search**: Helps users better understand indexed content\n- **Devin Wiki**: Automatically indexes repositories every few hours, generating comprehensive documentation including architecture diagrams, source links, and relevant details\n\n## Context & Background\n\n- Cognition AI's valuation doubled to **nearly $40 billion** by March 2025\n- The company faces growing competition from GitHub Copilot (free tier), Codeium Windsurf, and Amazon Q Developer\n- Enterprise clients include Goldman Sachs, Citibank, and financial technology company Ramp\n\n---\n\n**Note**: While my searches didn't return specific results for February 2025 updates, this may indicate that:\n1. No major updates were released in February 2025 specifically\n2. The updates were incremental/improvements to Devin 1.2 rather than a standalone release\n3. The information may not be widely documented in publicly accessible sources\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, I recommend checking Cognition AI's official channels or website directly.\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
