xtension references from Chinese documentation sites\n3. The official changelog site, but without specific February 2025 details in the preview\n\n### Recommendation:\nTo get the exact February 2025 changelog for the Continue VS Code extension, you should:\n1. Visit **https://changelog.continue.dev/** directly for the complete release notes\n2. Check the **GitHub repository** at **https://github.com/continuedev/continue** for detailed commit history and releases\n3. Look at the VS Code Marketplace page for the Continue extension for version history\n\nWould you like me to perform a more targeted search for specific features or changes you're interested in?\n\n\nREMINDER: You MUST include the sources above in your response to the user using markdown hyperlinks."
