   - Announced integration of Claude 3.5 Sonnet and Gemini 1.5 Pro
   - Move beyond exclusive reliance on OpenAI's GPT models

3. **GitHub Copilot - Vision Feature** (February 8, 2025)
   - VS Code v1.98 update added image-based interactions
   - Allows uploading screenshots/diagrams for code generation
   - Academic research showed mixed user experiences with productivity boosts but increased verification overhead

